NAME
    gcloud ml speech operations wait - poll long-running speech recognition
        operation until it completes

SYNOPSIS
    gcloud ml speech operations wait OPERATION [GCLOUD_WIDE_FLAG ...]

DESCRIPTION
    Poll a long-running speech recognition operation until it completes. When
    the operation is complete, this command will display the results of the
    transcription.

POSITIONAL ARGUMENTS
     OPERATION
        The ID of the operation to wait for.

GCLOUD WIDE FLAGS
    These flags are available to all commands: --account, --configuration,
    --flatten, --format, --help, --log-http, --project, --quiet, --trace-token,
    --user-output-enabled, --verbosity. Run $ gcloud help for details.

API REFERENCE
    This command uses the speech/v1 API. The full documentation for this API
    can be found at: https://cloud.google.com/speech/

NOTES
    These variants are also available:

        $ gcloud alpha ml speech operations wait
        $ gcloud beta ml speech operations wait

